CONTRIBUTION

1. Building
    - Minimum Golang Version is 1.10.2
    - Always use dep vendor.
    - Use `make all` to build and run

2. Formatting / Code Style
    Code style must be simple, and straightforward.
    Every change made must be formatted:
    - HTML
        4 Spaces instead of Tab
        Use double quote instead of single for Javascript and HTML Attribute
    - Golang
        Always use GOFMT before commiting.

3. Pull Request
    To create pull request, you can fork, create branch, and make pr.
    Since now we do not use any CI, we will manually pull and test.
    And do not push any binary, image, or any other.